						<a href="/services/cloud" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
					</div>
					
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="service-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Advanced Cybersecurity</h3>
						<p>Industry-specific security strategies that safeguard sensitive data, ensure compliance, and maintain seamless business operations.</p>
						<a href="/services/security" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
					</div>
					
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="service-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline></svg>
